         * Nom abrégé....: xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx                     *
         * Adresse.......: xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx *
         *                 xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx *
         *                 xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx *
         *                 xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx *
         * Code Postal...: xxxxxxx                                  *
         * Téléphone.....: xxxxxxxxxxxxx                            *
         * Fax...........: xxxxxxxxxxxxx                            *
         ************************************************************
@ENDIF
